                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="p-4 font-bold text-gray-900">Where You Live</td>
                            <td class="p-4">Bosses can live in any country. You do not have to be in the UK.</td>
                            <td class="p-4">We check your ID online.</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
